	<metadata>
		<title>Hello world Addon</title>
		<description>
			Enter addon description here
		</description>
	</metadata>
	
	<model>
		<property name="Text" type="string"/>
	</model>
	
	<view>
		<p>Hello ${mytext}</p>
	</view>
	
	<presenter>
		function Addon982_create(){
			
			var presenter = function(){}

			presenter.run = function(view, model){
				
				var element = view.getElementsByTagName('p')[0];
				var text = element.innerHTML;
				text = text.replace('${mytext}', model['Text']);
				element.innerHTML = text;
			}

			return presenter;
		}
	</presenter>
	
</addon>
